To inherit custom fiscal years in CRM Analytics, first enable the setup option for your org.
Select Inherit the custom fiscal year defined in Salesforce Setup, and then click Save.
When selected, CRM Analytics displays fiscal date values and filters based on the custom fiscal year defined in Salesforce Setup.
